PhpTaskDaemon Usage
===================

* Command Line
* State Api


Command Line
------------
A command line tool is provided to start, stop and monitor the daemon. Below a 

Command line:
* Start:        ./daemon --help
* Start:        ./daemon --action start
* Stop:         ./daemon --action stop
* Status:       ./daemon --action status
* Monitor:      ./daemon --action monitor


State Api
---------
The state (tasks status & statistics) of the daemon can be requested using the
following api call.

  $state = new \PhpTaskDaemon\Daemon\State::getState();
  var_dump($state);
